<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:24:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>线上券商富途、UP Fintech暂停美股夜盘交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/online-brokerages-futu-up-fintech-suspend-night-trading-us-stocks-2024-08-06/</link><description>以帮助中国投资者购买全球股票而闻名的在线券商富途控股和UP Fintech Holding已告诉客户，在全球市场波动加剧后，美国股票的夜盘交易将于周二暂停。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/online-brokerages-futu-up-fintech-suspend-night-trading-us-stocks-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动推出 AI 视频应用程序，加入 OpenAI Sora 竞争对手行列</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-joins-openais-sora-rivals-with-ai-video-app-launch-2024-08-06/</link><description>字节跳动扩大了其可根据文本提示生成视频的软件产品范围，加入了越来越多的中国科技公司的行列，进入了ChatGPT创建者OpenAI也瞄准的新兴市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-joins-openais-sora-rivals-with-ai-video-app-launch-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>Zalando 将在中国开设科技网站；目前没有进入市场的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zalando-open-tech-site-china-no-current-plans-enter-market-2024-08-06/</link><description>Zalando 周二表示，将在中国科技中心深圳开设一个新的科技网站，但目前不打算将其市场扩展到中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zalando-open-tech-site-china-no-current-plans-enter-market-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：过山车市场，日经指数反弹 10%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:07:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：随着关税的临近，记号笔制造商纽厄尔将更多业务从中国转移</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sharpie-maker-newell-moves-more-operations-china-tariffs-loom-2024-08-06/</link><description>记号笔制造商纽厄尔品牌公司(Newell Brands)首席执行官克里斯·彼得森(Chris Peterson)在接受路透社采访时表示，由于美国总统大选前面临关税的“不确定性”，纽厄尔品牌公司正在将厨房用具的生产迁出中国，并将书写业务的生产迁至田纳西州。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sharpie-maker-newell-moves-more-operations-china-tariffs-loom-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>华为与北京汽车推出首款联合开发的电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-huawei-baic-motor-launch-first-jointly-developed-ev-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国科技集团华为和北京汽车周二推出了首款联合开发的电动汽车（EV）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-huawei-baic-motor-launch-first-jointly-developed-ev-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利消息人士称，中国东风汽车有望在意大利建汽车厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利知情人士周二表示，意大利政府与中国东风汽车集团关于在意大利建设汽车工厂的谈判已进入后期阶段。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:46:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国城市遭遇创纪录高温，水稻种植区受到威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-megacity-limits-outdoor-lighting-record-heat-strains-grid-2024-08-06/</link><description>极端高温烘烤了中国东部沿海地区的大城市，并急剧增加了对家庭和办公室降温的电力需求，而中国内陆地区的炎热气温引发了人们对水稻作物受损的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:05:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-megacity-limits-outdoor-lighting-record-heat-strains-grid-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团第二季度表现强劲，因美国反弹超过中国疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-posts-32-rise-revenue-per-room-q2-2024-08-06/</link><description>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团报告称，由于美国的强劲反弹抵消了中国的疲软，第二季度每间可用客房的收入增长了 3.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-posts-32-rise-revenue-per-room-q2-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>舍弗勒第二季度利润下降近30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</link><description>德国机器和汽车零部件制造商舍弗勒公司周二报告称，由于轴承和工业解决方案部门（尤其是欧洲和中国）盈利下滑，第二季度核心利润下降近30%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，全球贸易好转提振中国七月出口扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-expanded-july-lifted-by-global-trade-upturn-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国7月份的出口可能会以更快的速度攀升，因为制造商受益于全球商品贸易持续好转带来的订单增加，预计这将保持出口强劲并缓解关税恐慌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 05:31:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-expanded-july-lifted-by-global-trade-upturn-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国公司在等待美国新的限制措施时囤积高端三星芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-stockpile-high-end-samsung-chips-they-await-new-us-curbs-say-2024-08-06/</link><description>三名消息人士称，华为和百度等中国科技巨头以及初创公司正在囤积三星电子的高带宽内存（HBM）半导体，因为预计美国将限制向中国出口芯片。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 04:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-stockpile-high-end-samsung-chips-they-await-new-us-curbs-say-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>台股暴跌后反弹 台积电收涨8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-stocks-rebound-after-plunge-quickly-pare-gains-2024-08-06/</link><description>台湾股市周二收高，摆脱周一创纪录的暴跌，合约芯片制造商台积电上涨 8%，但由于投资者对科技公司和美国经济前景的担忧挥之不去，市场情绪仍保持谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-stocks-rebound-after-plunge-quickly-pare-gains-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球市场反弹的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-quotes-2024-08-06/</link><description>全球股市周二上涨，部分扭转了前一天的部分大幅跌幅，而在央行官员发表了所有正确的言论来安抚投资者的紧张情绪后，日元稍作喘息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-quotes-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>尽管区域性反弹，中国股市、人民币仍趋于缓和；银行抛售导致收益率上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-struggle-rebound-after-global-markets-slump-2024-08-06/</link><description>尽管区域性反弹，但中国股市周二跌至六个月低点，人民币兑美元汇率也从周一的七个月高点回落，挑战了中国资产将成为全球市场暴跌的避风港的观点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-struggle-rebound-after-global-markets-slump-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>